description: Product Description Our sheet masks are pre-infused with time-tested actives. So if you have dehydrated or thirsty skin it will love this mask which seals your skin and lets the ingredients give your skin a major hit of moisture. Like Hyaluronic & Betaine which hydrate + plump up your skin and botanical actives Cucumber & Aloe Vera, lovely little soothers for natural dewy skin! Ingredients Aqua, Glycerin, Portulaca Oleracea (Purselane) Extract, Pogostemon Cablin (Patchouli) Oil, PEG-40 Hydrogenated Castor Oil, Tocopherol, Dipotassium Glycyrrhizate, Hyaluronic Acid, Carbomer, Triethanolamine, Methylparaben. Directions Apply to clean & dry skin, ensuring its smoothed out over the skin. Sit back and chill for 20 to 30 minutes. See more
